### What "Edge AI Generality" Means

Edge AI encompasses every application where data is generated and processed locally, without cloud round‑trips. This includes:

- **Sensors** (temperature, vibration, image, audio, chemical)
- **Actuators** (motors, valves, displays, alarms)
- **Interfaces** (voice, vision, haptics, biometrics)
- **Networks** (mesh, LPWAN, satellite, underwater)

ST‑T1024 runs on any edge device that can host a RISC‑V core with 0.7 MB SRAM and a coin‑cell battery. This is **every modern microcontroller**.

